  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "Having our upstairs box room refurbished. Neil came over and firstly removed all the historic wall paper (layers of it) and then saved us money on a plasterer by carefully filling and sanding everywhere that needed it. He decorated the room fully, including the walls, ceiling, woodwork and the radiator. Neil did a really good job! He’s also a really good guy; professional and also personable. I would definitely recommend him for any decorating jobs you have.",
      "reviewer": "Sachin",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Neil is a true professional with attention to detail. He is very friendly and a perfectionist with his paint work.\nNeil helped us pick our perfect shade of paint for our living room by coming up with a few suggestions.\nI highly recommend Neil you can tell he has a passion in what he does. Looking forward to him coming back in the future!\n5*",
      "reviewer": "J",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Neil did a great job for us. Lovely paint finish. He is very professional and courteous. He works well around the needs of his customers. Would have no hesitation to recommend.",
      "reviewer": "Simon",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Neil did a great job decorating our bedroom, he is friendly and professional with good communication and attention to detail. We will use him again",
      "reviewer": "Amrik",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Neil was absolutely brilliant. Very professional and high quality of workmanship. Highly Recommend\nThank you",
      "reviewer": "Caroline",
      "rating": 5
    }
  ],
